---
layout: base
title: "Sponsor nullEDGE 2026 | Partnership Opportunities"
description: "Connect with ServiceNow folks through authentic, community-focused events. Explore sponsorship packages for nullEDGE 2026."
permalink: /sponsors/
ogImage: /assets/og-images/page-sponsors-preview.png
schema: CollectionPage
breadcrumb:
  parent: Home
  parentUrl: /
  current: Sponsors
faqs:
  - question: "Do sponsors get attendee contact lists?"
    answer: "No. We don't sell or share attendee contact lists. nullEDGE is a community conference, not a lead-generation business."
  - question: "How do I generate leads then?"
    answer: "Through genuine engagement at your virtual booth. Run giveaways, offer value like free trials or white papers, host booth demos. These leads are higher quality because people chose to engage with you."
  - question: "What metrics do sponsors receive?"
    answer: "Aggregate event data: total attendance, booth visit counts, engagement rates, session attendance, and chat mentions. All metrics are aggregated and anonymized."
  - question: "Can I sponsor multiple events?"
    answer: "Yes! We have four global conferences in 2026. Multi-event sponsors get year-round homepage presence, priority booth placement, bundled pricing, and multiple speaking opportunities."
---

<div class="container wrapper flow">
  {# Hero Section #}
  <section class="prose text-center">
    <h1>Partner with nullEDGE 2026</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Connect with ServiceNow folks through authentic, community-focused events across four global conferences.
    </p>
  </section>

  {# Sponsorship Tiers - Dynamic from Fourthwall #}
  <section id="packages" class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Sponsorship Tiers</h2>
    
    <div class="tiers-grid">
      {% for sponsor in fourthwallSponsors %}
      <div class="tier-card{% if sponsor.bestValue %} tier-featured{% endif %}">
        {% if sponsor.bestValue %}<span class="badge badge-primary">Best Value</span>{% endif %}
        <h3>{{ sponsor.label }}</h3>
        {% if sponsor.price %}
        <p class="tier-price">${{ sponsor.price.value | thousands }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="tier-benefits">{{ sponsor.description | safe }}</div>
        <a href="mailto:{{ meta.email }}?subject={{ sponsor.emailSubject | urlEncode }}{% if sponsor.emailBody %}&body={{ sponsor.emailBody | urlEncode }}{% endif %}" class="btn btn-primary">
          {% if loop.first %}Get Started{% else %}Contact Us{% endif %}
        </a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-muted">
      Need something custom? Multi-event sponsorships, year-round presence, or other arrangementsâ€”<a href="mailto:{{ meta.email }}?subject=Custom%20Sponsorship%20Discussion">let's talk</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  {# FAQ #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2>Sponsor FAQ</h2>
    <dl class="faq-list">
      {% for faq in faqs %}
      <div class="faq-item">
        <dt>{{ faq.question }}</dt>
        <dd>{{ faq.answer }}</dd>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </dl>
  </section>

  {# Donations #}
  <section id="donations" class="region flow text-center">
    <h2>Support the Community</h2>
    <p>Want to help keep nullEDGE free for all attendees?</p>
    <a href="https://shop.thenulledge.com/pages/donate" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
      Donate Now
    </a>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-l);
    margin: var(--space-l) 0;
  }

  .tier-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: var(--space-l);
    background: hsl(var(--card));
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tier-featured {
    border-color: hsl(var(--primary));
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px hsl(var(--primary));
  }

  .tier-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs) 0;
    font-size: var(--size-step-2);
  }

  .tier-price {
    font-size: var(--size-step-3);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: hsl(var(--primary));
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-m) 0;
  }

  .tier-benefits {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-l) 0;
    text-align: left;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .tier-benefits li {
    padding: var(--space-xs) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
  }

  .tier-benefits li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .faq-list {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: var(--space-m) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
  }

  .faq-item dt {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item dd {
    margin: 0;
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
  }

  .text-muted {
    color: hsl(var(--muted-foreground));
  }
</style>
